> 
> ### Name: compare_lp_methods
> ### Title: Compare LP Solvers on the Same Problem
> ### Aliases: compare_lp_methods
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> obj  <- c(2, 3)
> A_ub <- matrix(c(1, 1, 2, 1), nrow = 2, byrow = TRUE)
> b_ub <- c(4, 6)
> cmp  <- compare_lp_methods(obj, A_ub, b_ub)
> cmp$summary_df
          method    obj_value iterations runtime_sec  status
1        simplex 0.000000e+00          0           0 optimal
2      two_phase 0.000000e+00          1           0 optimal
3 interior_point 5.804145e-09         17           0 optimal
