> ### Name: summarize_lp
> ### Title: Print a Human-Readable Summary of an LP Problem
> ### Aliases: summarize_lp
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> obj  <- c(2, 3, 1)
> A_ub <- matrix(c(1, 2, 1, 2, 1, 3, 1, 1, 1), nrow = 3, byrow = TRUE)
> b_ub <- c(14, 14, 8)
> summarize_lp(obj, A_ub, b_ub)
=== LP Problem Summary ===
Variables          : 3
Inequality (<=)    : 3
Equality           : 0
Objective direction: MIN

min  2x1 + 3x2 + x3
subject to:
  x1 + 2x2 + x3  <=  14
  2x1 + x2 + 3x3  <=  14
  x1 + x2 + x3  <=  8
  x1 >= 0, x2 >= 0, x3 >= 0
========================== 
